'''爱德华·克雷文·沃克'''（{{bd|1918年|7月4日|2000年|8月15日}}）是[[熔岩灯|熔岩灯]]的发明者。<ref name="Telegraph">{{cite news|title=Craven Walker|date=19 August 2000|publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1353253/Craven-Walker.html|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2013-09-02|archive-date=2013-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130902171836/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/obituaries/1353253/Craven-Walker.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Smithsonian">{{cite web|title=The History of the Lava Lamp|first=Abigail|last=Tucker|url=http://www.smithsonianmag.com/arts-culture/The-History-of-the-Lava-Lamp-191900581.html|publisher=Smithsonian magazine|date=March 2013|accessdate=28 February 2013|archive-date=2013-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103042259/http://www.smithsonianmag.com/arts-culture/The-History-of-the-Lava-Lamp-191900581.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYT">{{Cite web | title = Edward C. Walker, Lava Lamp Designer and a Naturist, Is Dead at 82 | last = Iovine | first = Julie V. | work = nytimes.com | date = 27 August 2000 | accessdate = 2016-03-02 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2000/08/27/nyregion/edward-c-walker-lava-lamp-designer-and-a-naturist-is-dead-at-82.html | quote =  | archive-date = 2016-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307144957/http://www.nytimes.com/2000/08/27/nyregion/edward-c-walker-lava-lamp-designer-and-a-naturist-is-dead-at-82.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 战争经历 ==
克雷文在[[二战|二战]]时是一名飞行员，驾驶[[蚊式轰炸机|蚊式轰炸机]]在德国上空避开未武装的飞机拍摄照片。<ref name="Telegraph"/>他在空军基地遇到了他的第一任妻子，玛乔丽·贝文·琼斯, 她当时正同[[辅助女子空军军团|WAAF]]在一起。克雷文在战争结束后继续驾驶飞机。

== 死亡 ==
接近1990年代末，克雷文与[[癌症|癌症]]进行着斗争，他于2000年在Dorset Matchams（南安普顿附近）去世，并葬在新森林的一块小墓地，享年82岁。<ref name="Telegraph"/>

